snippet.title: Try Dying Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Try Dying is a PvP party game where your goal is to DIE FIRST! Choose your cutest water dragon and hang out with your friends in noose, catch knives, and hug dynamite. And don't forget to stop your buddies who try dying!

Wishlist Try Dying on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2493920?utm_source=YT
